\c 19
\s Imithetho yobungcwele
\p
\v 1 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasikhuluma kuMozisi isithi:
\v 2 Tshono kunhlangano yonke yabantwana bakoIsrayeli uthi kubo: Banini ngcwele, ngoba mina iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wenu ngingcwele\x + 11.44,45. 20.7,26. 1 Pet. 1.16.\x*.
\p
\v 3 Yesabani, ngulowo lalowo, unina loyise\x + Eks. 20.12.\x*. Gcinani-ke amasabatha ami. NgiyiN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wenu\x + 19.30. Eks. 20.8.\x*.
\p
\v 4 Lingaphendukeli ezithombeni\x + 26.1; 1 Lan. 16.26. Hlab. 96.5. Isa. 2.20. 31.7.\x*, lingazenzeli onkulunkulu ababunjwe ngokuncibilikisa\x + Eks. 34.17.\x*. NgiyiN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wenu.
\p
\v 5 Njalo nxa linikela umhlatshelo weminikelo yokuthula eN\nd kosi\nd*ni\x + 7.15-18.\x*, liwunikele ukuze lemukeleke\x + 1.3; 22.19.\x*.
\v 6 Uzadliwa ngosuku lokunikela kwenu langakusasa; kodwa okuseleyo ngosuku lwesithathu kuzatshiswa ngomlilo.
\v 7 Uba kudliwa lokudliwa ngosuku lwesithathu, kuzakuba yisinengiso; kakuyikwemukeleka\x + 7.18.\x*.
\v 8 Ngakho okudlayo uzathwala ububi bakhe, ngoba ungcolise okungcwele kweN\nd kosi\nd*\x + 5.1.\x*; lalowomphefumulo uzaqunywa usuke ebantwini bawo\x + Eks. 30.33.\x*.
\p
\v 9 Lalapho livuna isivuno selizwe lakini, ungavuni ngokupheleleyo umngcele wensimu yakho; futhi ungabuthi okuseleyo kwesivuno sakho\x + 23.22; Dute. 24.19,20,21; Ruthe 2.15 16.\x*.
\v 10 Ungakhothozi isivini sakho; futhi ungabuthi okuwileyo kwesivini sakho; uzakutshiyela abayanga labemzini. NgiyiN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wenu.
\p
\v 11 Lingebi\x + Eks. 20.15.\x*, lingaphathi ngenkohliso, lingaqambi manga omunye kumakhelwane wakhe\x + Gen. 18.15. Levi 6.2.3.\x*.
\p
\v 12 Lingafungi ngamanga ngebizo lami\x + 6.3. Eks. 20.7.\x*, loba ungcolise ibizo likaNkulunkulu wakho. NgiyiN\nd kosi\nd*\x + 18.21.\x*.
\p
\v 13 Ungacindezeli umakhelwane wakho\x + 6.2,4.\x*, unga\add m\add*phangi. Iholo loqhatshiweyo lingahlali kuwe ubusuku kuze kube sekuseni\x + Dute. 24.14,15; Mal. 3.5; Jak. 5.4.\x*.
\p
\v 14 Ungaqalekisi isacuthe\x + Eks. 21.17.\x*, ungafaki isikhubekiso phambi kwesiphofu\x + Dute. 27.18.\x*, kodwa wesabe uNkulunkulu wakho. NgiyiN\nd kosi\nd*\x + 19.32. Gen. 42.18.25.17; Tshu. 5.7; 12.13; 1 Pet. 2.17.\x*.
\p
\v 15 Ungenzi ukungalungi ekwahluleleni; ungemukeli ubuso bomyanga, ungahloniphi ubuso bomkhulu, yahlulela umakhelwane wakho ngokulunga\x + Eks. 23.2,3. Dute. 1.17; 16.19. Hlab. 82.2. Zaga 24.23. Dute. 27.19. Jak. 2.9.\x*.
\p
\v 16 Ungahambahambi \add njeng\add*omnyundi phakathi kwabantu bakini\x + Zaga 11.13. 20.19. Hez. 22.9. Jer. 6.28; 9.4. Eks. 23.1,7; Hlab. 15.3. 50.20.\x*; ungamelani legazi lomakhelwane wakho. NgiyiN\nd kosi\nd*\x + Eks. 23.1,7. 1 Kho. 21.13. Mat. 26.60,61.\x*.
\p
\v 17 Ungazondi umfowenu enhliziyweni yakho\x + 1 Joha. 2.9,11. 3.15.\x*; umkhuze lokumkhuza umakhelwane wakho, ungathwali isono ngenxa yakhe\x + Mat. 18.15. Luka 17.3. Gal. 6.1.\x*.
\p
\v 18 Ungaphindiseli, ungabi \add lasikhwili\add* labantwana babantu bakini\x + Dute. 32.35. Zaga 20.22; Roma 12.17,19; Heb. 10.30.\x*; kodwa thanda umakhelwane wakho njengalokhu uzi\add thanda wena\add*. NgiyiN\nd kosi\nd*\x + Mat. 5.43. 22.39. Mat. 19.19. Mark. 12.31. Luka 10.27. Roma 13.9. Gal. 5.14. Jak. 2.8.\x*.
\p
\v 19 Gcinani izimiso zami. Ungavumeli izifuyo zakho zikhwelwe yimihlobo emibili. Ungahlanyeli insimu yakho ngenhlobo ezimbili\x + Dute. 22.9,10.\x*. Lesigqoko esemihlobo emibili exubeneyo singezi phezu kwakho\x + Dute. 22.11.\x*.
\p
\v 20 Lendoda, nxa ilala ngokwenyama lomfazi, eyisigqilikazi esikhombileyo, esingahlengwanga lokuhlengwa, kumbe singanikwanga inkululeko, kuzakuba lesijeziso. Kabayikubulawa, ngoba sasingakhululwanga.
\v 21 Njalo izaletha umnikelo wayo wecala eN\nd kosi\nd*ni, emnyango wethente lenhlangano, inqama ibe ngumnikelo wecala\x + 5.15; 6.6,7.\x*.
\v 22 Njalo umpristi uzayenzela inhlawulo yokuthula ngenqama yomnikelo wecala phambi kweN\nd kosi\nd* ngesono sayo esonileyo, izathethelelwa-ke esonweni sayo esonileyo.
\p
\v 23 Lalapho selifikile elizweni, lihlanyele yonke \add imihlobo\add* yezihlahla zokudla, lizathatha isithelo sazo njengento engasokwanga; iminyaka emithathu sizakuba singasokwanga kini, singadliwa\x + Eks. 6.12.\x*.
\v 24 Kodwa ngomnyaka wesine sonke isithelo sazo sizakuba ngcwele, sibe yindumiso eN\nd kosi\nd*ni.
\v 25 Langomnyaka wesihlanu lingadla isithelo sazo, ukuze zilengezelelele isivuno sazo. NgiyiN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wenu.
\p
\v 26 Lingadli \add lutho\add* olulegazi\x + 3.17.\x*. Lingenzi imilingo\x + Dute. 18.10; 2 Kho. 17.17. Gen. 30.27.\x*, lingachasisi ngemibono\x + Dute. 18.14. 2 Kho. 21.6. 2 Lan. 33.6.\x*.
\v 27 Lingageli amagumbi ekhanda lenu, ungoni amagumbi endevu zakho\x + 21.5. Isa. 15.2. Jer. 9.26; 48.37.\x*.
\v 28 Lingazicabi enyameni yenu ngenxa yofileyo, lingafaki phezu kwenu uphawu lokuzisika. NgiyiN\nd kosi\nd*\x + 21.1,4,5,11,19. Dute. 14.1; Jer. 16.6; 48.37.\x*.
\p
\v 29 Ungangcolisi indodakazi yakho ngokuyenza ibe liwule, hlezi ilizwe liphinge, lelizwe ligcwale inkohlakalo\x + Dute. 23.17.\x*.
\p
\v 30 Gcinani amasabatha ami\x + 19.3; 26.2.\x*, lihloniphe indlu yami engcwele. NgiyiN\nd kosi\nd*\x + Tshu. 5.1.\x*.
\p
\v 31 Lingaphendukeli kulabo abalamadlozi lakwabalumbayo; lingabadingi ukuze lingcoliswe yibo. NgiyiN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wenu\x + 20.6,27. Dute. 18.11; 1. Sam. 28.3,7,9; 1 Lan. 10.13. Isa. 8.19. Eks. 22.18. Seb. 16.16.\x*.
\p
\v 32 Sukumela impunga\x + Zaga 20.29.\x*, uhloniphe ubuso bomdala\x + 19.15; Eks. 23.3.\x*, wesabe uNkulunkulu wakho. NgiyiN\nd kosi\nd*\x + 19.14.\x*.
\p
\v 33 Futhi nxa owezizweni ehlala njengowezizwe lawe elizweni lakini, lingamcindezeli\x + Eks. 22.21. 23.9.\x*.
\v 34 Owezizweni ohlala njengowezizwe lani uzakuba kini njengozalwa elizweni phakathi kwenu\x + Eks. 12.48,49; Levi 17.15.\x*, umthande njengalokhu uzi\add thanda wena\add*; ngoba lalingabezizweni elizweni leGibhithe. NgiyiN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wenu\x + Dute. 10.19; Levi 19.18.\x*.
\p
\v 35 Lingenzi ukungalungi ekwahluleleni\x + 19.15.\x*, ebudeni\x + Eks. 26.2.\x*, esisindweni\x + Gen. 24.22.\x*, lesilinganisweni\x + Hez. 4.11,16.\x*.
\v 36 Banini lezikali zokulinganisa ezilungileyo\x + Dute. 25.13,15.\x*, izilinganiso ezilungileyo, \w i-efa\w** elilungileyo\x + Eks. 16.36.\x*, \w lehini\w** elilungileyo\x + Eks. 29.40.\x*. NgiyiN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wenu owalikhupha elizweni leGibhithe.
\v 37 Ngakho gcinani zonke izimiso zami lezahlulelo zami zonke, lizenze. NgiyiN\nd kosi\nd*\x + 18.4,5.\x*.